      "title": "Alla Odessi' to run for two more days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior official of the Railway Department said that the 'Ella Odyssey' train, which started as an inter-city weekend luxury train from Colombo, will run on Thursdays and Fridays from the 8th and 9th of this month.",
        "It is a remarkable feature to stop and donate this train running to Badulla, a railway destination that has won high tourist attraction."
      ],
